title: Cooling System
description: Maintenance activities for Cooling System in POWER TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Cooling System


## Operation

- Fan/Pump Oper.
- Flow Test


## Control

- Temperature Control
- Stage Activation


## Monitoring

- Alarm System
- Radiator Check
- Efficiency
